title: AirParrot 1.5 for Mac
description:
With AirParrot, send your computer screen to your TV screen without any extra wires. Present to groups, watch movies or play games. AirParrot puts you in charge of the big screen.

System Requirements
Mac
PC
OS X 10.6.8 or later
Apple TV 2 or Apple TV 3 running the latest OS updates
*Jailbroken devices are not supported. Not all features are available on all systems

Mac: 1.5   Size: 4.9 MB

Specific Technical Specifications

Intel Core 2 Duo or better ,1+GB RAM

Certain MacBooks are not compatible with third-party video drivers such as AirParrot. Installing the drivers on these computers could cause issues:

MacBookPro5,5
(13-inch, Mid 2009), NVIDIA GeForce 9400M

MacBookPro5,4
(15-inch, 2,53 GHz, Mid 2009), NVIDIA GeForce 9400M

MacBookPro5,3
(15-inch, Mid 2009) NVIDIA GeForce 9600M GT, GeForce 9400M

MacBookPro5,1
(2.53 GHz Intel Core 2 Duo) with both NVIDIA GeForce 9400M and NVIDIA GeForce 9600M GT

Network Specifications

Wireless 802.11g or greater. 802.11n or ethernet strongly recommended.

Many corporate and educational networks are split into segments called subnets. AirParrot must run on a computer in the same subnet as the desired connecting device. Bonjour and mDNS multicast traffic must also be enabled.
